description near the image, in the same fashion as if you cite a photograph.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/article&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><author>openmaptiles</author><guid isPermaLink="false">https://github.com/openmaptiles/openmaptiles</guid><pubDate>Mon, 10 Feb 2020 00:01:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>mapbox/node-sqlite3 #2 in PLpgSQL, This week</title><link>https://github.com/mapbox/node-sqlite3</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;i&gt;Asynchronous, non-blocking SQLite3 bindings for Node.js&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div id="readme" class="md" data-path="README.md"&gt;&lt;article class="markdown-body entry-content p-5" itemprop="text"&gt;&lt;p&gt;Asynchronous, non-blocking &lt;a href="https://sqlite.org/" rel="nofollow"&gt;SQLite3&lt;/a&gt; bindings for &lt;a href="http://nodejs.org/" rel="nofollow"&gt;Node.js&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://nodei.co/npm/sqlite3/" rel="nofollow"&gt;&lt;img src="https://camo.githubusercontent.com/228148f50621b4e41eb13e0fab6eb14760815d26/68747470733a2f2f6e6f6465692e636f2f6e706d2f73716c697465332e706e673f646f776e6c6f6164733d7472756526646f776e6c6f616452616e6b3d74727565" alt="NPM" data-canonical-src="https://nodei.co/npm/sqlite3.png?downloads=true&amp;amp;downloadRank=true" style="max-width:100%;"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://travis-ci.org/mapbox/node-sqlite3" rel="nofollow"&gt;&lt;img src="https://camo.githubusercontent.com/33f7e72209e6633f587714c31ec851e720a9aa9f/68747470733a2f2f7472617669732d63692e6f72672f6d6170626f782f6e6f64652d73716c697465332e7376673f6272616e63683d6d6173746572" alt="Build Status" data-canonical-src="https://travis-ci.org/mapbox/node-sqlite3.svg?branch=master" style="max-width:100%;"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a href="https://ci.appveyor.com/project/Mapbox/node-sqlite3" rel="nofollow"&gt;&lt;img src="https://camo.githubusercontent.com/c43fe5f120e298ec8c5482eadc8f287017223afe/68747470733a2f2f63692e6170707665796f722e636f6d2f6170692f70726f6a656374732f7374617475732f67766d37756c3068706d646177716f6d" alt="Build status" data-canonical-src="https://ci.appveyor.com/api/projects/status/gvm7ul0hpmdawqom" style="max-width:100%;"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a href="https://coveralls.io/github/mapbox/node-sqlite3?branch=master" rel="nofollow"&gt;&lt;img src="https://camo.githubusercontent.com/9ae55054d2e2aad6aeca10e35356466d3e73094e/68747470733a2f2f636f766572616c6c732e696f2f7265706f732f6d6170626f782f6e6f64652d73716c697465332f62616467652e7376673f6272616e63683d6d617374657226736572766963653d676974687562" alt="Coverage Status" data-canonical-src="https://coveralls.io/repos/mapbox/node-sqlite3/badge.svg?branch=master&amp;amp;service=github" style="max-width:100%;"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a href="https://david-dm.org/mapbox/node-sqlite3" rel="nofollow"&gt;&lt;img src="https://camo.githubusercontent.com/085afebe6cd6dccf7f4d39ed45b46219dad5dc54/68747470733a2f2f64617669642d646d2e6f72672f6d6170626f782f6e6f64652d73716c697465332e737667" alt="Dependencies" data-canonical-src="https://david-dm.org/mapbox/node-sqlite3.svg" style="max-width:100%;"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
